							</span>
						</span>
					</a>

					<a href="https://github.com/toddbirchard/linkbox" class="github-card" data-github="toddbirchard/linkbox">
						<h3 class="repo-title">linkbox</h3>
						<p class="repo-description">Generates a JSON object containing link preview information by passing a URL parameter.</p>
